<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="Страница-1" id="l1gKpsHPr0Btt2oKQ3zg">
    <mxGraphModel grid="1" page="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\nskinparam style strictuml\nskinparam sequence {\n  ParticipantBackgroundColor LightCyan\n  ParticipantBorderColor DarkCyan\n  LifeLineBorderColor DimGray\n  ArrowColor #333333\n}\n\ntitle Sequence Diagram: Обработка на AI заявка (RAG &amp; Fallback)\n\nactor \&quot;Потребител\\n(React UI)\&quot; as User\nparticipant \&quot;API Controller\\n(.NET)\&quot; as API\nparticipant \&quot;PromptSafety\\nService\&quot; as Safety\nparticipant \&quot;Retrieval &amp;\\nWeather Services\&quot; as Data\nparticipant \&quot;AiProviderClient\\n(Gemini)\&quot; as Gemini\nparticipant \&quot;AiProviderClient\\n(OpenAI)\&quot; as OpenAI\nparticipant \&quot;Response\\nComposer\&quot; as Composer\n\nUser -&gt; API: POST /api/assistant/chat\\n{ \&quot;message\&quot;: \&quot;Времето на Витоша?\&quot; }\nactivate API\n\n&#39; 1. Проверка за сигурност\nAPI -&gt; Safety: ValidatePromptAsync(message)\nactivate Safety\nSafety --&gt; API: ValidationResult (IsSafe = true)\ndeactivate Safety\n\n&#39; 2. Извличане на контекст (RAG)\nAPI -&gt; Data: BuildContextAsync(query)\nactivate Data\nnote right of Data\n  Извършва хибридно търсене (eco.json),\n  проверява Provenance Policy\n  и извлича метеорологична прогноза.\nend note\nData --&gt; API: EnhancedContext (Trails + Weather)\ndeactivate Data\n\n&#39; 3. Опит с основния AI модел\nAPI -&gt; Gemini: GenerateReplyAsync(Context + Prompt)\nactivate Gemini\n\nalt Успешен отговор от Gemini\n    Gemini --&gt; API: aiResponse\nelse Грешка / Timeout (Fallback Policy)\n    Gemini --&gt; API: ProviderException\n    deactivate Gemini\n    \n    note over API, OpenAI: Активиране на PromptTemplateFailOpen\n    \n    API -&gt; OpenAI: GenerateReplyAsync(Context + Prompt)\n    activate OpenAI\n    OpenAI --&gt; API: aiResponse\n    deactivate OpenAI\nend\n\n&#39; 4. Пост-обработка\nAPI -&gt; Composer: FormatResponse(aiResponse)\nactivate Composer\nnote right of Composer\n  Парсва отговора и добавя\n  Schema.org структурирани данни\nend note\nComposer --&gt; API: StructuredResponseDTO\ndeactivate Composer\n\n&#39; 5. Връщане към клиента\nAPI --&gt; User: HTTP 200 OK\\n{ StructuredResponseDTO }\ndeactivate API\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="rY-htpEFwPSCVnB__rQ0-1">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="735" width="1271" x="20" y="20" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
